<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='808000' id='t-808000'>HE: Almost none.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='810000' id='t-810000'>It's no different</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='812000' id='t-812000'>than sending a text.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='814000' id='t-814000'>It's no different than checking an email.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='817000' id='t-817000'>It's one of those things, we got by just fine before we had to do any of those.</span>
